content.html: Fun fact: erectile dysfunction risk is approximately 6 times higher in men who have had COVID. If you’re using Nicki Minaj’s cousin’s friend’s roommate’s uncle’s supposedly swollen balls to avoid getting the vaccine, may the odds be ever in your favor.
